DESCRIPTION FRANCAISE

Description principale
Nom de la map : 	ba_jail_electric_max_v4
Mappeur :		MaX
Style de la map :	ba_jail
Taille de la map : 	12.9 Mo
( Musique dans la map : Hitsuji Mix de Hitsuji  ) 
( Téléchargement (7.39 Mb) : http://www.megaupload.com/?d=MW1FJ5SF )

Description de la map 
Nombre de spawn T : 	23
Nombre de spawn CT :	16
1 cage, 1 isoloire, 1 discothèque, 1 terrain de foot, 10 prisons normales, 1 prison de riche, 
8 prisons de pauvre, 1 piscine, 1 simulateur de chute libre.

Petite description :

Cette map est une reconstitution de ba_jail_electric_large mais beaucoup de changements
sont présents.
La piscine reste à sa place, l'infirmerie aussi, le garage est remplacé par une discothèque
et la cuisine par un terrain de foot. Derrière la cage se trouve un simulateur de chute
libre.
Beaucoup de passages secrets, d'armes sont cachés dans cette map.

Merci de télécharger cette map.
___________________
ENGLISH DESCRIPTION 
___________________

Map name :	ba_jail_electric_max_v4

Description of the map
Spawn T :		23
Spawn CT :	16
1 cage, 1 disco, 1 soccer, 10 prisons, 1 rich prison, 8 poor man prisons, 1 pool, 1
simulator of free-fall

Little description :

This map is a reconstitution of baçjail_electric_large but there are a lot of changes !
The pool is always here, infirmary too, garage is a disco and the kitchen is a soccer.
Behind the cage, there is a simulator of free-fall.
A lot of secret passages are hidden in this map.

Thanks to download.

Hey!

This is my second released Jail Map.
It's called ba_jail_dusty_BETA3 because the Map is based on ba_electric_razor.v6.
I tried to optimized the Map as much as possible.
It have High FPS(100-180) and it has a good Gameplay.
I recommened to play this Map with up to 30 Players.

It has 25 terrorist spawns, 20 counter-terrorist spawns.

So,Enjoy it! ;)

Hello everyone

This is a a 60-70% completetion preveiw of my map "Delirium"
It is 100% playable with the exception of a few basic jailbreak elements ie: The weapons in the cells.

You can see my video log here:
http://www.youtube.com/user/shinoteseu

And the feedback Forums here:
http://www.xtremejailbreak.com.au/home/forums/viewtopic.php?f=19&t=3012&start=0
http://www.xtremejailbreak.com.au/home/forums/viewtopic.php?f=19&t=2963

If you have any strong experience in mapping and wish to contribute where possible then add my steam account: Shinoteseu

Please don't add my steam account to give feedback.

This version contains the following:

95% finished gunroom
90% finished pool (known as the grotto)
100% finished kitchen and mess hall (may go back and add anyway)
95% finished deagle toss.
95% finished Time attack
100% finished sewers
80% finished cells
65% finished main room

These are just gauged statistcs though
I may alter things as i see fit.

I still have 2 rooms to go and then i need to build 2 vent systems, and then possibly a series of walkways to intergrate the rooms. Thanks to the underground theme of the map i have no real horizontal or vertical limitations. And by limitations i mean i don't need to add visual explainations to the size of the prison.

Other than that detail and decals can't hurt anything.

This map will quite hopefully be exclusive to the Xtreme jailbreak servers in australia, I don't mind the preveiw versions being used on minor servers since i plan to make the full version something that no other preveiw version will have.
